# GanttGen — Project Context

GanttGen is a zero-installation, single-file React web application for professional project management and Gantt chart generation. It runs entirely in the browser (including on the `file://` protocol) with no backend, no server, and no installation. The final output is a single `index.html` bundled by `vite-plugin-singlefile`.

Key capabilities: Excel import/export (SheetJS), Critical Path Method (CPM/slack calculation), interactive Gantt chart (SVG/Canvas), dynamic theming with CSS variables, WBS with expandable rows, milestone diamonds, baseline bars, dependency arrows, and working-days calculation.

Tech stack: React, Tailwind CSS, `xlsx`, `lucide-react`, `html-to-image`, Vite + `vite-plugin-singlefile`.

